ObjectClass.Name: AutoMech
ObjectClass.Description:
MECH: Mechanical light armor and AA support Powerful against air unit groups Inaccurate vs ground
Builds advanced structures Detects cloaked units

Objective.Name: Move
Objective.Details: \Move to specified location \Move Speed: 3, MaxInc: 45\Vision Range: 24, Aggro Radius: 30

Objective.Name: Attack
Objective.Details: Attack target or Attack-Move to location \ \[Weapons Avg Damage/10secs ]\Gnd: 60, R 21, Sta C\Air: 30, R 18, SR 4, Sta S

Objective.Name: Patrol
Objective.Details: Hold CTRL and select up to 5 points to\continuously patrol around\Target one of your own units to HOLD\current position or select a single\location to HOLD that position

Objective.Name: Change Commander
Objective.Details: \Set this unit's commander\ \Alt-Right-Click on unit to\select its current commander

Objective.Name: Remove from Hierarchy
Objective.Details: \Remove unit from hierarchy\to disconnect from commander\and all subordinates

Objective.Name: Priority
Objective.Details: \While Moving or Attacking,\subordinates will break formation\and move at their top speeds

Objective.Name: Build
Objective.Details: \Select a building to create:\ \TURRET, MACROFAB, CHRONOPORTER,\SLINGSHOT, TELEPORTER, CARRIER

Objective.Name: Stop
Objective.Details: \Interrupt current objective\and return to idling

Objective.Name: Slingshot
Objective.Details: Small building\Automatically Teleports idle units to a \preset location within a short distance\Can move itself

Objective.Name: Teleporter
Objective.Details: Medium building\Allows units to Teleport to any\location within a medium distance

Objective.Name: Defense Turret
Objective.Details: Small building\Breaks TSS\Detects cloaked units\Splash damage weapon(self-upgradable)\[Weapon] Ground:57(+8) Air:105(+15)

Objective.Name: Macrofab
Objective.Details: Produces the following units:\MAR, FRIGATE, MFB, BLACKBIRD,\HEAVY CRUISER\Equips HEAVY CRUISER with nukes

Objective.Name: Defense Turret
Objective.Details: Not Available \ Requires the Machinery\ upgrade at the ARMORY

Objective.Name: Slingshot
Objective.Details: Not Available \ Requires the Gate Tech\ upgrade at the ARMORY

Objective.Name: Chronoporter
Objective.Details: Medium building\Transports units through time\Creates TSS (Temporal Soliton Shield)

Objective.Name: Teleporter
Objective.Details: Not Available \ Requires the Gate Tech\ upgrade at the ARMORY

Objective.Name: Chronoporter
Objective.Details: Not Available \ Requires the Gate Tech\ upgrade at the ARMORY

Objective.Name: Carrier
Objective.Details: Fast air mechanical armor\Carries air and ground units\Heals/repairs carried units\Splash damage weapon\[ Weapon ] Ground: 221 Air: 168

Objective.Name: Carrier
Objective.Details: Not Available \ Requires the Aerospace\ upgrade at the ARMORY\ Requires an active COMM CENTER

Objective.Name: Importer
Objective.Details: emergency Importer creation\ \Marines create Importers\using less resources

Objective.Name: Armory
Objective.Details: emergency Armory creation\ \Marines create Armories\using less resources

Objective.Name: Chronoport
Objective.Details: Not Available\ Requires the Gate Tech\ upgrade at the ARMORY

Objective.Name: Teleport
Objective.Details: \Teleport to a specified location\ Must be near a Teleporter

Objective.Name: Chronoport
Objective.Details: \Chronoport to a specified time\ Must be near a Chronoporter
